Declare $fields property to fix PHP 8.2+ dynamic property deprecation.

Upstream Block.php assigns $this->fields in the constructor without ever
declaring the property, which triggers a Deprecated notice on every Block
subclass under PHP 8.2+.

--- a/src/Block.php
+++ b/src/Block.php
@@ -103,6 +103,14 @@
     protected $enabled = true;
 
     /**
+     * The ACF fields registered for the block.
+     *
+     * @since 0.1.0
+     * @var array $fields
+     */
+    protected $fields = [];
+
+    /**
      * Begin block construction!
      *
      * @since 0.10
